<h1 id="title">John Calvin</h1>
  <h2 id="subtitle"> Theological giant of his time.</h2>
  <h3 id="tribute-info">Short list of John Calvins accomplishments:</h3>
  <section id="general-info">
  <ul>
    <li>Wrote the Institutes of the Christian Religion by the time he was 25</li>
    <li>Wrote biblical commentaries on every Old and New Testament book in the bible</li>
    <li> Changed the moral and spiritual direction of Geneva that stunned outsiders who visited the city</li>
   <li> Permenantly changed the political, spiritual, and religious direction of the nation of France from Catholic to Protestant</li>
  </ul>
  </section>
